text: The 2007 Asian Karate Championships are the 8th edition of the Asian Karate Championships, and were held in Nilai Indoor Stadium, Seremban, Malaysia from August 24 to August 26, 2007. ==Medal table== ==References== * Results Category:Asian Karate Championships Category:Sport in Malaysia Category:2007 in sports Category:2007 in Asia
